HEADWORD: Moro
<hw>Mo"ro</hw> <pr>(m⟦omac⟧"r⟦osl⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. It.
<ets>mora</ets> mulberry, L. <ets>morum</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>A small abscess or tumor having a resemblance to a mulberry.</def>
